327
00:27:02,340 --> 00:27:07,060
and taught us about life.

328
00:27:07,060 --> 00:27:10,580
Both knowledge and self-development wise.

329
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:13,620
And most importantly, about love.

330
00:27:15,040 --> 00:27:18,760
Love can make one's life to be fulfilled,

331
00:27:18,760 --> 00:27:22,160
at the same time, it can hurt, too.

332
00:27:39,940 --> 00:27:42,440
Hurting so much that some of you

333
00:27:43,030 --> 00:27:44,860
may be scared of falling in love.

334
00:27:47,730 --> 00:27:52,080
But I want all of you to know that,

335
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:57,840
if one day, you find yourself being in love,

336
00:27:57,840 --> 00:28:00,120
and whatever the reason may be,

337
00:28:01,580 --> 00:28:04,620
be honest with your feelings.

338
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:07,940
Do what your heart says.

339
00:28:09,820 --> 00:28:16,030
You might end up smiling, laughing,

340
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:22,080
but at least you'd have followed what your heart says.

341
00:28:23,560 --> 00:28:27,460
Don't be afraid of what the result might bring.

342
00:28:27,460 --> 00:28:31,940
What is important is that you have acted as your heart says.

343
00:28:33,580 --> 00:28:37,260
At least you won't regret not trying.

344
00:28:42,840 --> 00:28:45,339
Last but not least,

345
00:28:45,340 --> 00:28:49,800
I want every one of you to appreciate everything in your life.

346
00:28:50,340 --> 00:28:53,260
Not only the good things you've encountered,

347
00:28:54,100 --> 00:29:00,720
but also the bad things that happened.

348
00:29:01,840 --> 00:29:04,939
Because all these experiences

349
00:29:04,939 --> 00:29:09,240
shape who you are today.

350
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:10,960
Thank you.

351
00:29:47,620 --> 00:29:49,720
What are you doing alone?

352
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:56,540
