354
00:30:05,940 --> 00:30:10,480
It's my fault that I didn't dare to tell you the truth.

355
00:30:13,120 --> 00:30:14,860
Why?

356
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:22,040
I was scared that you'd not like me.

357
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:26,840
I didn't mean to lie to you.

358
00:30:29,660 --> 00:30:33,340
Yeah, I get you.

359
00:30:33,820 --> 00:30:35,800
I am sorry, too.

360
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:41,100
For throwing my temper out at you

361
00:30:41,100 --> 00:30:45,219
and not being willing to listen to you.

362
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:50,570
It's okay.

363
00:30:50,570 --> 00:30:53,240
You got your reasons.

364
00:30:57,460 --> 00:31:01,500
Why are you here anyway?

365
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:07,160
Because I knew that someone was here.

366
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:12,500
But you were gone for so long.

367
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:14,860
That's because I thought you were still mad.

368
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:17,980
So you didn't show up?

369
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:22,090
Well, here I am now.

370
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:33,940
Why are you all dressed up anyway?

371
00:31:33,940 --> 00:31:35,800
You can't even enter the prom.

372
00:31:35,800 --> 00:31:37,400
Oh, this?

373
00:31:38,320 --> 00:31:40,810
I don't want to be the odd one out.

374
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:45,620
And it looks like I came for the prom.

375
00:31:59,360 --> 00:32:03,780
For the past few days, I was trying to discover

376
00:32:04,560 --> 00:32:08,360
