377
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:12,500
But I couldn't find it.

378
00:32:14,260 --> 00:32:18,630
But whatever the reason is,

379
00:32:18,630 --> 00:32:21,040
I don't care anymore.

380
00:32:22,800 --> 00:32:26,620
I just love you.

381
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:39,160
I love you, too.

382
00:32:47,260 --> 00:32:48,939
What was that?

383
00:32:48,940 --> 00:32:52,740
