398
00:35:17,040 --> 00:35:18,800
So I came.

399
00:35:37,680 --> 00:35:39,880
Are you feeling all right?

400
00:35:43,180 --> 00:35:45,560
I would feel worse

401
00:35:46,270 --> 00:35:48,640
